Package dk.iha.plpa.multiparadigm

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FunctionPanel
    Creates a panel for typing in the scheme function.
    FunctionsFramePanel
    Panel which holds functions panels and the button to add more of them.
    Main
    Class for running the program and displaying error messages.
    MainFrame
    Sets up the window used for this program.
    Plotter
    The Plotter class is the main Panel of the Schemer graphing tool.
    RectanglePanel
    Panel to specify the input for calculating the area below the graph using the rectangle method.
    Schemer
    Contains all methods for calculations done in the Schemer graphing tool.
    SettingsPanel
    Settings panel shown in the bottom of the program screen.
    Tester
    A suite of automatic tests for the graphing tool Schemer.
